.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, dancing
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| Job           | police-officer | manager    |
| Birthday   | june        | november  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Hobby     | dancing            | traveling       |

