2 different pets are kept: hamster, horse
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the paramedic is on the left or right of the journalist##3
5. the paramedic is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
